<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 tmsk bạ̹ydy wtrfʿny ḥbk yạrby yrjʿny
 tnhḍly rwḥy .tsẖjʿny wtfyḍ ḥnạn
 brmy bạ̉ḥmạly ạ̉mạmk bḥsb wʿwdk wklạmk
 ygẖmrny bạlrạḥh slạmk rạḥh wạ̉mạn
 ạ̹nt ḥbyby .ạ̹nt nṣyby ạ̹nt ḥyạty wtrnymạty
 ḥạmy ḥyạty bswr mn nạr mn ạ̉y hjwm ạ̉w mn ạ̉kẖṭạr
 ạ̹nt mʿy kl ạlmsẖwạr ṭwl ạlzmạn
 rwḥk yạrby bymlạny tsbyḥ wtrnym wạ̉gẖạny
 ʿn ḥbk ạ̹nt ạ̹lly sbạny mn ạlhwạn</lyrics>
